finalData.name: THE EDIT
finalData.description: The Edit at Tower C is a luxury residential development by Meraas featuring 3 basements, a ground floor, and 33 floors. The project offers a total of 198 residential units ranging from 1 to 4-bedroom residences and a flagship penthouse. The building features extensive indoor and outdoor amenities, including double-height entrance lobbies, sky gardens on multiple levels, and a sky lounge.
